songs.lyrics:
[Hook]
What's up kiss the sky
What's up kiss the sky
Why would I come down before I'm gone, gone

[Verse 1: Mike Gao]
Look, I woke up feeling flyer than some mother fucking birds

songs.title: Kiss The Sky
